{"type": "article", "id": 31044, "title": "水果姐推出高跟鞋，以及，Supreme 的秋冬造型一览 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-16T02:17:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7721, "name": "滑板"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 31548, "name": "Love Moschino"}, {"id": 250, "name": "Philippe Starck"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 6726, "name": "Katy Perry"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160816094524zqFTDRok78i1Ydeu.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/elizabeth-debicki-graces-cover-david-jones-magazine-10506624/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百货公司 David Jones 推出了 app 和杂志</b></a> | David Jones 是于 1838 年创建的澳大利亚最大的百货公司，此次推出了名为 Jones 的时尚季刊杂志以及 app。这本杂志将在  David Jones 位于澳洲的 40 家店铺内作为礼物送给购买了商品的顾客，也在其他报刊亭和书店进行贩售，价格为 9.95 澳元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/philippe-starck-starck-paris-launch-fragrance-collection-10506036/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>产品及建筑设计师 Philippe Starck 首次发布香水</b></a> |  Philippe Starck 于 2013 年 9 月与香水集团 Perfumes y Diseño 签署了合约，研制了三款名为 Starck 的香水，将于下周在美国高档百货连锁店 Neiman Marcus 正式发售。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/color-cosmetics/amber-rose-estee-lauder-flirt-donald-robertson-10507024-10507024/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛的创意总监 Donald Robertson 创办网红化妆品牌</b></a> | 在 instagram 上拥有 17.9 万粉丝的 Donald Robertson，日前宣布成立新的化妆品牌 Flirt Cosmetics，该品牌将于 9 月 15 日在其官网上发售。它的第一任代言人是拥有 1210 万粉丝的模特 Amber Rose。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/color-cosmetics/victoria-beckham-to-launch-limited-edition-color-cosmetics-with-estee-lauder-10505718/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Victoria Beckham 将与雅诗兰黛合作推出限定款彩妆</b></a> | 该系列彩妆将于 9 月 13 日在美国、英国发售。涵盖了 15 个产品，价格从 30 美元的唇膏到 1200 美元的面霜不等。雅诗兰黛拒绝透露对这系列彩妆销售预期。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/earnings/jcpenney-q2-earnings-loss-2016-revenue-profit-sales-footwear-shoes-248304/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国连锁百货 J.C. Penney 第二季度亏损情况有所好转</b></a>&nbsp;| J.C. Penney 公布第二季度业绩，净损 5600 万美元，去年同期亏损 1.17 亿美元。公司预估全年销售将同比升至 4%，有望实现盈利。&nbsp;<br></p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/fashion/designers/katy-perry-shoes-collection-launch-global-brands-group-248949/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Katy Perry 要与 Global Brands Group 合作推出女士鞋款</b></a> | 日前，Katy Perry 与 Global Brands Group （利标集团）正式签署了合约，将推出个人同名女士鞋类。其中涵盖了拖鞋、运动鞋和高跟鞋等多个类别，售价为 59-299 美元，将于 2017 年 2 月正式发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816101332pGr5yofAdHMjO924.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816101326J0NeYcUfFM2QLPzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816101309FtDVRIXMy3WALuUC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">草图</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></h3><p>日本时尚杂志《GRIND》打造 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/grind-y-3-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 2016 秋冬系列造型特辑</a>。这次的特辑是以科幻为主题的，使用不规则剪裁重塑运动服。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091603kRNxrIy7hQwVD5lB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091612IT38eqpt5MLz1EuV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091622xDhovUHmcnjIap6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">身兼 Volcom 滑板团队成员及 Anti-Hero 专业滑板选手的 Grant Taylor 与队友 Chris Pfanner 共同推出 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/volcom-x-anti-hero\" rel=\"nofollow\">Volcom x Anti-Hero 联名系列滑板</a>，使用了“老鹰”商标作为设计核心，此系列即将开售。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091647QL4xJCM8dtlomXYg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091655TdjLzWYZDVeFBs9U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091704Mmd3bP7H8wKVsqfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">模特界新星 Victor Nylander 和 Ella Wennstrom 为<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/love-moschino-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Love Moschino 的 2016 秋冬系列</a>拍摄了一组广告大片，由摄影师 Giampaolo Sgura 掌镜。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091716SX1g9Z3lFQMoqhxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091727YQxHEObfdj5MlV83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608160917370IjyNAMeDaRhF3Ps.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Supreme 发布<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/supreme-2016-fall-winter-headwear\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2016 秋冬帽款系列</a>，多达几十种不同的设计，强调材质和色彩的丰富性。还加入了“宇航员” “Tom and Jerry” 等趣味元素。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091748Yw0jMsRCnQA8z1XK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091756Zr3BKO9qigeCdXfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081609180531jt5iyV6swgDpXa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091816QDA5ZOeuizCUNcg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091827wTIf92nyijsP5Q7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Supreme 发布 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/supreme-2016-fall-winter-preview\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬系列 lookbook </a>，主打色彩丰富的军事风，更是推出了与 Champion 的合作款外套。该系列将于 8 月 18 日在纽约、伦敦、巴黎等地开售，8 月 20 日登陆日本，8 月 25 日官网开售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816092103f6zJp8HRLv9ENXZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816092055AaFIKgZisxOQpP79.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816092045O1JvNi5Z0aQzoAlG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816092038cULGtOJ8AqKDVBNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081609203142EzLKeWD9iTgrdb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160816091902GdRkzE2yFI7lVuZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}